Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.26,0:02:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what darkness\Nmight lie ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.80,0:02:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I will rush into it headfirst!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.06,0:02:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.85,0:02:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I will get my hands\Non that power!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.28,0:02:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting late...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.52,0:03:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I sensed\Nsomeone there just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.40,0:03:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The lights...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't even close\Nto bedtime yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.96,0:03:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is this...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.00,0:03:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle... Aunt...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.81,0:03:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Father... Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.19,0:03:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Father? Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There's somebody in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.03,0:04:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.36,0:04:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.66,0:04:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Father! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother!\NFather and Mother are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? For what reason?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.03,0:05:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell would do\Nsomething like this...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.79,0:05:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother... what are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.55,0:05:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Big Brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You pathetic younger brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.40,0:06:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mangekyo Sharingan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.42,0:06:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me see\Nthis kind of thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.79,0:06:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother, why did you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother... Why did you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.91,0:07:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to measure my vessel...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.71,0:07:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,To measure your vessel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Only for that reason...\Nyou killed everybody...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.36,0:07:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.43,0:07:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.46,0:08:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't kill me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.84,0:08:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.15,0:08:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is too unlike you, Big Brother.\NI mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I acted as the big brother\Nyou desired was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,because I wanted to\Nmeasure your vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:09:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the potential\Nto become my opponent
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.91,0:09:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,in order for me to measure\Nmy vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You hated me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and you continued to have\Nthe desire to surpass me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.34,0:09:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly why\NI will allow you to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,for my own benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.35,0:09:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You are someone who could be able to use\NMangekyo Sharingan just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,However, on one condition...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.65,0:09:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That you must kill\Nyour closest friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You've gotta be kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.71,0:09:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.17,0:09:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Regarding Uchiha Shisui\Nwho committed suicide last night
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:10:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,by throwing himself into\Nthe Nakano River...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.77,0:10:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The other one that did not show up\Nto the meeting is Shisui...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you adored him like\Nhe was your real older brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.70,0:10:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That was... your doing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.16,0:10:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother, you... killed Shisui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.48,0:10:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right... and because of\Nthat I obtained these eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.08,0:10:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The main hall of Nakano Shrine...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Underneath the seventh tatami mat\Non the far right
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,is the secret gathering place\Nof the Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There you will find recorded\Nthe secret of...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.05,0:10:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the raison d'etre of\Nthe Uchiha Clan's Visual Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The secret of the raison d'etre...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you attain these eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you will become the third person\Nincluding myself
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:11:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,to utilize\Nthe Mangekyo Sharingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,then there will have been meaning\Nin my allowing you to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.96,0:11:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,However... at present...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not worth killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.59,0:11:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My pathetic younger brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to kill me,\Nthen begrudge me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And live in an ugly manner...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.97,0:11:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away... run away...\Nand cling to life...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.77,0:11:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And one day, when you have\Nthe same eyes as I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,come and stand before me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:11:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The only one who survived...\Nis that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.15,0:12:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't he have\Nan older brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.86,0:12:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but he's gone missing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be true...\NThat elite Uchiha Clan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Sasuke! What did you\Ncome to buy today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke, are you on your way to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.23,0:13:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw Itachi earlier,\Nbut he's very admirable, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already become\Na top-class Shinobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:14:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He graduated from the Ninja Academy\Nat the top of his class at age seven
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and attained the rank\Nof Chunin at age ten, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He was able to use Sharingan\Nwhen he was eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.43,0:14:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy is truly the pride\Nof the Uchiha Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.89,0:14:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home... Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.09,0:15:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.02,0:15:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.78,0:15:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why only Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.33,0:16:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Your brother's your brother.\NAnd you are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Father cares deeply\Nabout both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The main hall of Nakano Shrine...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.10,0:17:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Located underneath\Nthe seventh tatami mat on the far right
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.31,0:17:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,is our clan's secret gathering place...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... So that's what it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shikamaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna go to the candy shop\Nafter school?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do that 'cuz\Nyour mother's nice,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but if my mother found out that I bought\Nmyself a snack before going home,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.18,0:17:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be in big trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear the news...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.68,0:17:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that entire Uchiha Clan\Nwas apparently murdered?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, my dad told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently he's the only one\Nwho survived...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.96,0:18:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,With me, you're all\Nyour father talks about...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.26,0:18:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder... what kind of things\NFather was saying to Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.74,0:18:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Begrudge me! Hate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.79,0:18:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's for the purpose of killing you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.67,0:18:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I will rush headfirst into whatever\Ndarkness which may lie ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:19:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I will obtain that power no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,From this point onwards,\NI am an avenger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.31,0:19:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke is now\Nin depths of darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.86,0:19:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If you stop in a place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.82,0:19:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you won't be able to catch up\Nwith Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.01,0:19:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Neji, it's just like you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.51,0:19:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy looks like he's in\Nthe depths of darkness right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.93,0:19:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He really hit me with\Nhis full strength! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you consider me...\Nyour comrade any longer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.65,0:20:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't all those things we did together\Nin Squad Seven mean anything to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.79,0:20:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.21,0:20:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I will get my hands on\Nthat power no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't meaningless...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, you became my...\Nclosest friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.47,0:20:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We've become... friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.98,0:20:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.44,0:20:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All the more reason why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All the more reason why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.36,0:20:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,there's meaning in taking\Nyou down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.28,0:20:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't fully understand but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.16,0:20:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I understood that you want to\Nfight me with your everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.58,0:20:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke...!
Comment: 0,0:21:08.05,0:21:08.09,ED9,,0,0,0,,ED Start
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.55,0:21:18.38,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}When I recalled the parts one by one,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:24.75,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}I felt as though I had understood everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.75,0:21:35.32,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}Faded words which I kept so close to me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.63,0:21:45.10,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}Speechless nights, a hint of warmth,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.85,0:21:51.84,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}and this distant yearning for you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.15,0:22:01.15,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}I live, simply repeating this cycle
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.33,0:22:12.86,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}Held in my two hands is a droplet of time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.31,0:22:23.31,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}Softly clutching forgotten memories, lost words
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.19,0:22:37.11,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}{\fad(0,2500)}I'll keep these thoughts...
Comment: 0,0:22:38.03,0:22:38.06,ED9,,0,0,0,,ED End
